seo: 通达OA,任意文件下载,视频文件漏洞
seo_en: Tongda OA, arbitrary file download, video file vulnerability
summary: 检测通达OA v2017中video_file.php文件存在的任意文件下载漏洞，攻击者可能利用此漏洞读取服务器敏感文件
summary_en: Detect the arbitrary file download vulnerability in the video_file.php file of Tongda OA v2017. Attackers may exploit this vulnerability to read sensitive files on the server.
